Description:
LOW MAINTENANCE ELEGANCE WITH NO BODY CORP!!
Ray White Dandenong is proud to present this fantastic opportunity for all First home buyers, downsizing and astute investors looking to be nestled in a highly sought-after pocket of Dandenong. This well-maintained home is within a short distance to all amenities and provides the convenient and ideal lifestyle you have been searching for.
For all investors out there, potential rental return is $300 - $330pw.
Offering 2 very good-sized bedrooms with BIR, a spacious family area, dining/meals area which is adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped with electric cooking, dishwasher and an abundance of cupboard space. The main bathroom, separate toilet and laundry make up the interior of this lovely home.
This home also includes a spacious courtyard which is ideal for all year round entertaining.
Features include: Aircon, wall heater, courtyard, ceiling fans, roller shutters, single lockup garage and much more.
Located within a stone's-throw away from Dandenong South Primary School, Dandenong Station, Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, Dandenong Creek walking trail, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
With the location and features like these, we would highly recommend you act soon before you see a SOLD sticker on the board!!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!
*PHOTO I.D. REQUIRED UPON INSPECTION*

Large & liveable - 4 bedrooms plus study!
Lots of room for all the family with the bonus of a large rectangular block of 700m2 (approx). This double storey home is perfect for large families featuring a downstairs formal lounge and dining area with open fireplace and is north facing with lovely bay window.
There are 3 bedrooms downstairs with the main bedroom having ensuite access to an elaborate fully tiled bathroom featuring spa bath, bidet and a glass brick wall which fills the room with natural light.
The modern kitchen with island bench also offers an oversized gas upright stove and oven. The rumpus room opens onto a covered alfresco entertaining area looking over the large rear garden.
Upstairs features 2 bedrooms with balcony access and both are serviced by a 2nd bathroom with toilet. A long paved driveway leads to a huge double tandem garage and workshop. A separate studio or gym room could also be converted to home office.
Additional features such as ducted heating, evaporative cooling, solar hot water and solar panels are offered throughout.
Positioned on such a large parcel of land the future re-development potential of this property should not be overlooked. Popular and convenient location in Dandenong within minutes to Monash Freeway, Dandenong Plaza and Market. St. Johns College and Dandenong High are both within easy distance.

Description:
Location, Location, Location!
This double storey, three-bedroom townhouse is not only easy on the eye, its easy on the feet too, making it a convenient place to set up home in an excellent suburb with great walkability. Just moments away, youll find Dandenong North Primary School, Dandenong High School, Hemmings Park, Dandenong Skate Park, and the huge Dandenong Plaza which features a great selection of stores and a handy market to stock up on fresh produce.
Theres also a vast array of cafes and restaurants nearby, more parks, a medical/dental centre and veterinary hospital,and bus transport metres from the doorstep. Youll hardly need to use the car, but the highway is easily accessible for when you do.
With attractive street appeal, this modern house will feel like home as soon as you step inside. The open plan layout flows effortlessly and lends itself well to entertaining, or just relaxing with the family, in the spacious living and dining areas. The open plan kitchen adjoins the large family/meal room and features stone benchtops, a gas cooktop, and dishwasher. There is also a second living zone for entertaining guests or relaxing with a movie. An internal laundry is also conveniently located on the lower floor.
Moving upstairs, youll spot the master suite which benefits from a generouswalk-in robe and a sleek ensuite with double vanity. The remaining two bedrooms with built-in robes are of a good size and share a central family bathroom with separate WC. Further highlights includeducted heating, evaporative cooling,reverse cycle air conditioner to living room, high ceilings, LED downlights, and a mixture of tile and timber look flooring throughout.
Low maintenance is the theme of the tidy outside area which consists of a private rear courtyard with water tank and shed for extra storage. Perfect for relaxing summer evenings! The single garage adjoins the house with off-street parking available on the driveway.
This double storey delight makes daily life simple and will undoubtedlybe snapped up quickly. Dont miss out!

Surprising with it's presentation, space and improvements that have given it a new lease on life, this first floor apartment provides a great lifestyle home or investment opportunity in a central Dandenong location within walking distance of shopping, dining, entertainment and transport. Perfectly maintained throughout its life, the home features floating floors and light paint tones throughout, a spacious living/dining area with electric heater and a renovated kitchen with electric oven and cook top. There are 2 bedrooms with built in wardrobes as well as a neat bathroom with included laundry facilities, a separate toilet plus a titled car space in the ground floor carport that has remote gate access.
**Photo id required for all open for inspections**

Description:
Under Instructions from the Mortgagee!
This solid brick Californian bungalow is well built home is a testament to the early 1900's and with a renovation would emanate the romance of yesteryear. The home features 12 foot ornate ceilings and Baltic pine floor boards throughout. There is a lounge at the front of the home with an adjoining formal dining room. There are 3 bedrooms and a bathroom centrally located to service the whole house. The kitchen at the rear has an adjoining walk-in pantry and there is a 3rd room at the rear of the house, suitable as a study. The location would make it attractive to further develop for either apartments or Townhomes (S.T.C.A) or a Medical Centre (S.T.C.A). Close to Dandenong Secondary College, Chisholm TAFE and Dandenong Hospital, you can't go wrong!
This is a rare opportunity that should not be missed!
Terms: 10% Deposit, Balance 30 Days

Description:
Stylish Townhouse In The Heart Of Dandenong
Centrally located in one of the most popular pocket of Dandenong, close to schools shops and major arterials this spacious and modern town house will surprise you with its light filled rooms and great space. Featuring:
• Spacious living area with high ceiling and down lights
• Modern kitchen with overhead cupboard, dishwasher, plenty of storage space and overlooking dining area,
• Three spacious bedrooms with modern feature wall
• Spacious bathroom and separate toilet
• Spacious backyard with artificial grass and to enjoy BBQs with family and friends while watching the kids playing
• Extra features include ducted heating, split system air conditioner in lounge, downlights, floating floorboards, porcelain tiles, quality curtains, powder room, single remote controlled garage and parking space plus more!
Brilliantly located within walking distance to Primary and Secondary schools, Hemmings Reserve, Dandenong Pavilion, and close proximity to Dandenong Plaza and Market, Dandenong Hospital, public transport & all amenities!
Easy access to Princes Highway, Eastlink and Monash Freeway
Don't delay and call Yogi Patel on 0451 719 161 to book in an inspection.
Photo ID required for all opens.
